text: Medina Dešić (born 15 September 1993) is a German-born Montenegrin footballer who plays as a forward for Würzburger Kickers (formerly known as SC Würzburg Dragons) and the Montenegro women's national team. ==Early life== Dešić was raised in Erlenbach am Main. ==International career== Dešić made her senior debut for Montenegro in mid-January 2020 in a friendly match against Bosnia and Herzegovina. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Montenegrin women's footballers Category:Montenegro women's international footballers Category:German women's footballers Category:Footballers from Bavaria Category:People from Erlenbach am Main Category:German people of Montenegrin descent Category:2.
